{"tid":984835,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【名符其實Moon River】末日先兆？ 美河流出現巨型冰盤","createTime":"2019-01-17T06:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T01:08:18.000Z","uid":47272,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0da1037b189feed8052da84c1b621561c52419ea","tid":984835,"uid":47272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T06:14:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190117&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59151819\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190117%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59151819&d=c8V27Lgsxe1lABVcT2XcULZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=9cfd3bd4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190117%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59151819&h=cbee54af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190117&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59151819</a><br />\n（北美通訊）美國緬因州城巿Westbrook一條河流，出現直徑達300呎的巨型冰盤，圓形弧度近乎完美，引發民間迷信猜測。科學家強調，有關冰盤雖然罕見，但絕對是自然現象。<br />\n<br />\n今次出現的巨型冰盤，位於巿內的Presumpscot River，巿政府得悉奇觀出現後，周一即派員出動無人機作高空拍攝，製作短片，並於周二上載互聯網，引發民眾討論。有人認為冰盤呈完美圓形，極不自然，猜疑可能是「外星人侵襲地球」、「世界末日」先兆。有人則一笑置之，開玩笑說冰盤是雀鳥的「旋轉木馬」。<br />\n科學家相信，今次的巨型冰盤是由融雪掉進河流旋渦、在低溫下形成，並解釋冰塊在自轉時，因為會不斷撞到岩石或水流，所以被打磨成完美圓形，強調一切是自然而成。<br />\n<br />\n美國陸軍工兵隊（Army Corps of Engineers）轄下的寒冷地區研究與工程實驗室（Cold Regions Research and Engineering Laboratory）表示，美國每年都會錄得一至兩宗同類個案。加州理工學院物理系教授Kenneth Libbrecht指出，過去發現的河中冰盤，直徑只得20至30呎，相信今次發現的300呎巨型冰盤，有機會打破世界紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2ksx568r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2ksx568r&h=63638f8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n緬因州出現巨型冰盤，圓形弧度近乎完美，引發民間多種猜測。(美聯社)"},{"pid":"1e2f8800a4b1f539d528e4b2ff93a259fe734429","tid":984835,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:24:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee6e95eab12f85ddceaabfd965bf5e85c05e3367","tid":984835,"uid":146435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:37:59.000Z","msg":"不嬲都傳新51區係緬因州 美帝可能係試緊外星科技姐"},{"pid":"7b9da286832d3bca0b4b241ea5dbf5793038da70","tid":984835,"uid":170614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T15:33:26.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"14bb0bb37e1c55ac354cc5698ba840eaba1a48cd","tid":984835,"uid":23200,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T15:58:49.000Z","msg":"香港嘅美荷樓有冇反應"},{"pid":"2924de4f1c311ed2ee8632917d578d7b6878664a","tid":984835,"uid":39608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T01:00:50.000Z","msg":"圓到咁都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61fe577a075a8b9cee612cb7c87845429625e1c0","tid":984835,"uid":195646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T01:08:18.000Z","msg":"你地信唔信有地下城鎮"}]}